Package: deckglgeoarrow
Title: Use 'GeoArrow' to Add 'Deck.gl' Layers to a 'maplibregl'/'mapboxgl' Map
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Tim",
             family = "Appelhans",
             role = c("cre", "aut"),
             email = "tappelhans@tutamail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9824-2707")),
      person("RConsortium", 
